mm: convert a few VM_BUG_ON callers to VM_BUG_ON_VMA

Trivially convert a few VM_BUG_ON calls to VM_BUG_ON_VMA to extract
more information when they trigger.

[akpm@linux-foundation.org: coding-style fixes]
